Text:
@Noogieman and others;

In order to try another Product Key than the one you might have unsuccessfully entered, you need to open regedit (Start button>Search programs and files>regedit) and go to this folder using the panel on the left:

HKEY_CURRENT_USER\Software\Microsoft\Windows\CurrentVersion\WindowsAnytimeUpgrade

Right click on ProductKey, choose "Modify..." and enter your other key.
